             were indicted for <rs id="t18180506-103-off584" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180506-103-off584" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-103-off584" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180506-103-cd585" type="crimeDate">13th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180506-103-off584 t18180506-103-cd585"></join>, 35 yards of flannel, value 35s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18180506-103-victim892" type="victimName">
                     Humphrey 
                     Sexton
                  <interp inst="t18180506-103-victim892" type="surname" value="Sexton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180506-103-victim892" type="given" value="Humphrey"></interp>
